  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Randomized controlled trial (RCT) to evaluate the effectiveness of applying Purell速 (62%
      ethyl alcohol in emollient gel) to the penis of male partners of women diagnosed with BV for
      preventing BV recurrence after treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
