    <description>The male partner in each couple was asked to apply Purell速 to his penis at least daily, and immediately prior to and following intercourse. Couples received a brochure with information on control of STI and good hygienic practices. Brochures for intervention and control arms were similar except the intervention arm brochure provided information on how to use the study product (Purell速).</description>
